ActBoards of Trade Act
SubjectYorkton Chamber of Commerce (Saskatchewan) ** Change of Boundaries **
PrecisOrder approving the application by the YORKTON CHAMBER OF COMMERCE, in Saskatchewan, TO CHANGE THE BOUNDARIES OF ITS DISTRICT from the village of Yorkton and the electoral district of Yorkton as constituted by an ordinance of the Northwest Territories.
